c.UIL-MEDIUM-ICON-TOGGLE-BUTTON.ua.LABEL: Enable User Menu Choices for GUISLIDE
c.UIL-MEDIUM-ICON-TOGGLE-BUTTON.ua.TOGGLELABEL: Enable User Menu Choices for GUISLIDE

g2:Structure.g2:sa.UIL-BUTTON-LABEL-VALUE: Enable User Menu Choices for GUISLIDE

g2:c.PROCEDURE.g2:a.TEXT: _guislide-toggle-user-menu-choices (B: class uil-button, W: class item, D-or-W: class item) begin if (the toggle-state of B is on) then conclude that guislide-user-menu-choices-active is true else conclude that guislide-user-menu-choices-active is false; end

g2:c.USER-MENU-CHOICE.g2:a.LABEL: EDIT-SLIDER. . .
g2:c.USER-MENU-CHOICE.g2:a.CONDITION: ((the item I superior to the workspace of the item does not exist) or (the item X superior to the workspace of the item exists and X is a uil-dialog and the uil-origin of the uil-dialog superior to the workspace of the item = the symbol master) or (the item Y superior to the workspace of the item exists and Y is not a uil-dialog)) and guislide-user-menu-choices-active is true
g2:c.USER-MENU-CHOICE.g2:a.ACTION: start guide-setup-edit-grobj-dialog ("guislide-edit-slider", the item, this window) at priority uil-global-default-procedure-priority
